### 10. REQUEST CHANGE PASSWORD
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "current_password": "ValidPass4$",
  "new_password": "Joko1234$",
  "confirm_password": "Joko1234$"
}

### 11. FORGET PASSWORD REQUEST
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "email": "maya.kartika.sari@example.com"
}

### 12. VERIFY FORGOT PASSWORD OTP
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "email": "maya.kartika.sari@example.com",
  "otp_code": "725623",
